reviewText: This it is a poor VHS-dvd transfer. It doesn't worth it. Still you could watched but now that I have it, I wouldn't have paid more than 1$.

I'm a Derek Ford admirer. So what? Well ...
no need to say more, really, if you know not of what I write but
if you have seen other Derek Ford stuff
you may be a little disappointed but, though there is no Heather Deeley,
this is pure porno chic... bizarre porno chic
